  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841080/extras/537637a6ed21cc0d583f400ead1c02e7.poster.avif?t=1752454402\" width=426 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841080/extras/537637a6ed21cc0d583f400ead1c02e7.webm?t=1752454402\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841080/extras/537637a6ed21cc0d583f400ead1c02e7.mp4?t=1752454402\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quantum Velocity is a fast-paced, arcade-style 3D racing game set in a futuristic world. Race against up to 7 other players in  multi-player mode or AI opponents in single-player mode and compete for the top spot on the global online leaderboards. The game offers over 35 unique tracks and more than 200 vehicles to unlock.    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features currently in the game</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong>Single-player races with up to 8 AI opponents.</strong></i></u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong>Multi-player races with up to 8 other players.</strong></i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong>Global leaderboards to compete for the top spots.</strong></i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841080/extras/5eda22494a961be4f3dd3c3ec849c482.avif?t=1752454402\" width=320 height=74 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong>Over 200 unique vehicles to unlock, each with varying stats like Max Speed, Acceleration, Steering, and Braking. Find the one that suits your style!</strong></i></u><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841080/extras/a81440fcd72cf44bd2337e5f3c87ac2d.poster.avif?t=1752454402\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841080/extras/a81440fcd72cf44bd2337e5f3c87ac2d.webm?t=1752454402\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841080/extras/a81440fcd72cf44bd2337e5f3c87ac2d.mp4?t=1752454402\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><u>35+ different tracks to unlock each with unique music.</u></i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841080/extras/0f7e4cafc9884272f146278727aeae61.poster.avif?t=1752454402\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841080/extras/0f7e4cafc9884272f146278727aeae61.webm?t=1752454402\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841080/extras/0f7e4cafc9884272f146278727aeae61.mp4?t=1752454402\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><u>Enter the Galactic Arcade in the Extras and play 4 mini-games to win credits in.</u></i></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841080/extras/9514934d82f05b672f996dc600598955.poster.avif?t=1752454402\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841080/extras/9514934d82f05b672f996dc600598955.webm?t=1752454402\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841080/extras/9514934d82f05b672f996dc600598955.mp4?t=1752454402\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong>Galactic Music Player, featuring every music track in the game</strong></i></u><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841080/extras/9d3addecb2fcc8bfd5e8f5a76f5b92b9.avif?t=1752454402\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841080/extras_big/9d3addecb2fcc8bfd5e8f5a76f5b92b9.avif?t=1752454402 width=800 height=86 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong>Keyboard and partial controller support for racing (controller recommended). Mouse is used only for some menu interactions.</strong></i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841080/extras/82bd52f0d6d1a28c2bcf791518549fba.avif?t=1752454402\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841080/extras_big/82bd52f0d6d1a28c2bcf791518549fba.avif?t=1752454402 width=800 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i>Supports 16:9 resolutions only.</i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><u>Steam Achievements</u></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Planned Features for Early Access Development:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i>Additional tracks and vehicles.</i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i>Expanded controller support.</i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i>More in-game settings.</i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841080/extras/6d8f9a5a40d6f5b3bd5c46f1f740cb3d.poster.avif?t=1752454402\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841080/extras/6d8f9a5a40d6f5b3bd5c46f1f740cb3d.webm?t=1752454402\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841080/extras/6d8f9a5a40d6f5b3bd5c46f1f740cb3d.mp4?t=1752454402\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841080/extras/537637a6ed21cc0d583f400ead1c02e7.poster.avif?t=1752454402\" width=426 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841080/extras/537637a6ed21cc0d583f400ead1c02e7.webm?t=1752454402\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841080/extras/537637a6ed21cc0d583f400ead1c02e7.mp4?t=1752454402\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quantum Velocity is a fast-paced, arcade-style 3D racing game set in a futuristic world. Race against up to 7 other players in  multi-player mode or AI opponents in single-player mode and compete for the top spot on the global online leaderboards. The game offers over 35 unique tracks and more than 200 vehicles to unlock.    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features currently in the game</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong>Single-player races with up to 8 AI opponents.</strong></i></u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong>Multi-player races with up to 8 other players.</strong></i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong>Global leaderboards to compete for the top spots.</strong></i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841080/extras/5eda22494a961be4f3dd3c3ec849c482.avif?t=1752454402\" width=320 height=74 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong>Over 200 unique vehicles to unlock, each with varying stats like Max Speed, Acceleration, Steering, and Braking. Find the one that suits your style!</strong></i></u><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841080/extras/a81440fcd72cf44bd2337e5f3c87ac2d.poster.avif?t=1752454402\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841080/extras/a81440fcd72cf44bd2337e5f3c87ac2d.webm?t=1752454402\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841080/extras/a81440fcd72cf44bd2337e5f3c87ac2d.mp4?t=1752454402\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><u>35+ different tracks to unlock each with unique music.</u></i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841080/extras/0f7e4cafc9884272f146278727aeae61.poster.avif?t=1752454402\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841080/extras/0f7e4cafc9884272f146278727aeae61.webm?t=1752454402\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841080/extras/0f7e4cafc9884272f146278727aeae61.mp4?t=1752454402\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><u>Enter the Galactic Arcade in the Extras and play 4 mini-games to win credits in.</u></i></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841080/extras/9514934d82f05b672f996dc600598955.poster.avif?t=1752454402\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841080/extras/9514934d82f05b672f996dc600598955.webm?t=1752454402\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841080/extras/9514934d82f05b672f996dc600598955.mp4?t=1752454402\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong>Galactic Music Player, featuring every music track in the game</strong></i></u><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841080/extras/9d3addecb2fcc8bfd5e8f5a76f5b92b9.avif?t=1752454402\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841080/extras_big/9d3addecb2fcc8bfd5e8f5a76f5b92b9.avif?t=1752454402 width=800 height=86 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong>Keyboard and partial controller support for racing (controller recommended). Mouse is used only for some menu interactions.</strong></i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841080/extras/82bd52f0d6d1a28c2bcf791518549fba.avif?t=1752454402\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841080/extras_big/82bd52f0d6d1a28c2bcf791518549fba.avif?t=1752454402 width=800 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i>Supports 16:9 resolutions only.</i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><u>Steam Achievements</u></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Planned Features for Early Access Development:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i>Additional tracks and vehicles.</i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i>Expanded controller support.</i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i>More in-game settings.</i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841080/extras/6d8f9a5a40d6f5b3bd5c46f1f740cb3d.poster.avif?t=1752454402\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841080/extras/6d8f9a5a40d6f5b3bd5c46f1f740cb3d